<script type="text/javascript">
function getCustomStyle(logoBase64, headerBase64){
    var customStyle = '.Application_Logo { background: none !important; } .Organization_Logo { background-image: url("data:image/jpeg;base64,' + logoBase64 +'");  background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto 100%; margin-top: 3px; } .Organization_Background { background: url("data:image/jpeg;base64,' + headerBase64 +'");}';
    
    return customStyle;
}

// Replaces the APM SUFI logo
// WARNING: only works on webscreens with Layout: 'Layout\LayoutForm'
function addDomNodeClass(domSelector, className){
    var domNode = $(domSelector);
    if(domNode &amp;&amp; domNode.length) {
        if(!domNode.hasClass(className)){
            domNode.addClass(className);
        }
    }
}

// Replaces the APM SUFI logo
// WARNING: only works on webscreens with Layout: 'Layout\LayoutForm'
function replaceSufiLogo(){
    addDomNodeClass('div.Application_Logo&gt;a', 'Organization_Logo');
}

// Replaces the APM SUFI Background Image
// WARNING: only works on webscreens with Layout: 'Layout\LayoutForm'
function replaceSufiBackground(){
    addDomNodeClass('div.Application_Title', 'Organization_Background');
}

// Replaces the APM SUFI Header Theme
// Params:
// -&gt; logoBase64:   The Organization Logo image encoded in Base64
// -&gt; headerBase64: The Organization header background image encoded in Base64
function replaceSufiHeaderTheme(logoBase64, headerBase64){
    var oldCustomStyle = $('style[title="OrganizationStyle"]');
    //Remove the old Style to avoid repeats
    if(oldCustomStyle &amp;&amp; oldCustomStyle.length){
        oldCustomStyle[0].remove();
    }
    var style = document.createElement('style');
    style.type = 'text/css';
    style.title = 'OrganizationStyle';
    style.innerHTML = getCustomStyle(logoBase64, headerBase64);
    document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0].appendChild(style);
    replaceSufiLogo();
    replaceSufiBackground();
}
</script>
</div><div class="OSAutoMarginTop">
<script type="text/javascript">
replaceSufiHeaderTheme('','');
